sources.description:
Mystery Highway - Radio DJ George Bell does his weekly adventure drama series Mystery Highway. The stories come to life on screen in a series of science fiction and paranormal short films, as a group of truckers listen in, and imagine themselves in them.
2023.  Stars: Rachel Elizabeth Ames, Christopher Cendana, Randy Davison
